snippet.title: Miss Rosen's Wowtastic! Marching Band - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Join Miss Rosen's quirky marching band in a magical, story-driven puzzle game that blends a surreal narrative with vibrant, colorful puzzles, out now on the Nintendo eShop for Nintendo Switch!

Free demo also available at: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/miss-rosens-wowtastic-marching-band-switch/
